\n		\n\n	\n	\n	\n\n		English Conversation Circle – Bloor/Gladstone Library\n	\n\n\n					\n	\n		Bloor/Gladstone Library	\n	\n		1101 Bloor Street West\, Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada	\n	\n									\n\n				\n	Are you new to Canada as a Permanent Resident or a Convention Refugee? Practice English in small groups\, with the support of our Mentors! 8 weekly sessions Speak with confidence […] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Tue		\n		\n			3		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		English Conversation Circle – Daniel G. Hill	\n\n					\n		\n		March 3 @ 11:00 am - 12:30 pm	\n	\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n	\n\n		English Conversation Circle – Daniel G. Hill\n	\n\n\n					\n	\n		Daniel G. Hill Library	\n	\n		620 Jane Street\, Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada	\n	\n									\n\n				\n	Are you new to Canada as a Permanent Resident or a Convention Refugee? Practice English in small groups\, with the support of our Mentors! 8 weekly sessions Speak with confidence […] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Tue		\n		\n			3		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		Tax Filing – Information Session	\n\n					\n		\n		March 3 @ 11:00 am - 1:00 pm	\n	\n					\n	\n		CultureLink	\n	\n		2340 Dundas St W\, Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada	\n	\n									\n\n				\n	Come join us and prepare for the upcoming tax season! To register\, please email Alexandra at aerdeyli@culturelink.ca \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Tue		\n		\n			3		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		Looking For Volunteers: Content Creator Crew!	\n\n					\n		\n		March 3 @ 2:00 pm - 4:00 pm	\n	\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n	\n\n		Looking For Volunteers: Content Creator Crew!\n	\n\n\n					\n	\n		Parkdale Library	\n	\n		1303 Queen Street West\, Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada	\n	\n									\n\n				\n	Love TikTok + Instagram? Turn your creativity into real experience What you'll do: Take photos + short videos Capture behind-the-scenes moments Help edit Reels/TikToks (simple + guided) Support social media […] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Tue		\n		\n			3		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		Citizenship Education Circle – East Scarborough Storefront	\n\n					\n		\n		March 3 @ 2:30 pm - 4:30 pm	\n	\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n	\n\n		Citizenship Education Circle – East Scarborough Storefront\n	\n\n\n					\n	\n		East Scarborough Storefront	\n	\n		4040 Lawrence Ave East\, Scarborough\, ON\, Canada	\n	\n									\n\n				\n	Free weekly sessions for Newcomers who want to prepare for the Citizenship test! Learn about the test’s content and structure Get support and tips from our Volunteer Mentors Practice with […] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Tue		\n		\n			3		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		The Creative Den	\n\n					\n		\n		March 3 @ 3:00 pm - 4:30 pm	\n	\n					\n	\n		East Scarborough Storefront	\n	\n		4040 Lawrence Ave East\, Scarborough\, ON\, Canada	\n	\n									\n\n				\n	Come join us for FREE weekly meetups to enjoy hands-on arts and crafts activities. Let's make something together! For newcomers to Canada! Permanent Residents or Convention Refugees\, and at least […] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Tue		\n		\n			3		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		Youth Connect Hub	\n\n					\n		\n		March 3 @ 3:30 pm - 5:30 pm	\n	\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n	\n\n		Youth Connect Hub\n	\n\n\n					\n	\n		CultureLink Children & Youth Centre	\n	\n		3535 Dundas Street West\, Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada	\n	\n									\n\n				\n	A safe and welcoming space for youth to connect\, relax\, and have fun. Enjoy group games\, creative activities\, food sessions\, and conversations that support emotional well-being and confidence. For Newcomer […] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Tue		\n		\n			3		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		English Conversation Circle – Forest Hill Library	\n\n					\n		\n		March 3 @ 6:00 pm - 7:30 pm	\n	\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n	\n\n		English Conversation Circle – Forest Hill Library\n	\n\n\n														\n\n				\n	Are you new to Canada as a Permanent Resident or a Convention Refugee? Practice English in small groups\, with the support of our Mentors! 8 weekly sessions Speak with confidence […] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Tue		\n		\n			3		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		Citizenship Education Circle – Toronto Reference Library	\n\n					\n		\n		March 3 @ 6:00 pm - 8:30 pm	\n	\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n	\n\n		Citizenship Education Circle – Toronto Reference Library\n	\n\n\n					\n	\n		Toronto Reference Library	\n	\n		789 Yonge Street\, Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada	\n	\n									\n\n				\n	Are you new to Canada as a Permanent Resident or a Convention Refugee? Every Tuesday at the Toronto Reference Library there will be free weekly sessions to prepare for the […] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Wed		\n		\n			4		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n	Postponed\n\n\n	\n		Networking Event with TD Canada Trust	\n\n					\n		\n		March 4 @ 1:00 pm - 3:30 pm	\n	\n														\n\n				\n	Come join us for a networking session with TD Canada Trust! Who can participate: Internationally trained professionals Permanent Resident or Convention Refugee At least 19 years of age Job-ready English […] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n							\n				\n				\n\n	\n	\n		\n			Wed		\n		\n			4		\n	\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n	\n\n\n			\n\n				\n					\n	\n		Create Learn Connect	\n\n					\n		\n		March 4 @ 2:00 pm - 4:00 pm	\n	\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n	\n\n		Create Learn Connect\n	\n\n\n					\n	\n		Cecil Street Community Centre	\n	\n		58 Cecil Street\, Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada	\n	\n									\n\n				\n	Nurture Your Artistic Potential! Our thoughtfully designed Art Workshops encourage creativity\, focus\, and growth Participants must be a Permanent Resident or Convention Refugee and at least 19 years old. To […] \n\n				\n			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n			\n		\n\n		\n	\n		\n	\n		\n	\n\n		\n			Previous Events		\n	\n\n\n		\n	\n		Today	\n\n\n		\n	\n		\n			Next Events		\n		\n	\n\n	\n\n	\n\n\n		\n	\n		\n			\n				Subscribe to calendar			\n			\n	\n\n		\n		\n			\n									\n\n	\n		Google Calendar	\n\n									\n\n	\n		iCalendar	\n\n									\n\n	\n		Outlook 365	\n\n									\n\n	\n		Outlook Live	\n\n									\n\n	\n		Export .ics file	\n\n									\n\n	\n		Export Outlook .ics file
